aa(lp315
VLastly I want to say that
p316
aVall of you, probably,
p317
aVhave had some relationship at some time in your life
p318
aVwith a dog, a cat, some sort of pet,
p319
aVand you recognized that those are individuals.
p320
aVAnd some of you consider them almost part of your family.
p321
aVIf you had a relationship with a penguin,
p322
aVyou'd see it in the same sort of way.
p323
aVThey're amazing creatures
p324
aVthat really change how you view the world
p325
aVbecause they're not that different from us:
p326
aVThey're trying to make a living,
p327
aVthey're trying to raise their offspring,
p328
aVthey're trying to get on and survive in the world.
